name: KÂSHÂN ROSE - COLOGNE
description:
SPECTACULAR, SOPHISTICATED, UNEXPECTED

KÂSHÂN ROSE 
90ml Refillable Bottle

Contemporary Haute Parfumerie created by Jean-Claude Ellena and Thierry De Baschmakoff.

The Eternal East:
A surprising fragrance, this floral eau de toilette embodies a Persian Rose, celebrated during a Rose Festival in May in the city of Kashan, the first oasis in the region. The scent comes along with fruity and spice fresh head notes (lychee, cardamom and Rose Berries). The floral heart unveils a sublime Rose which reflects a thousand years know how. The ambrette seed bring altogether a reassuring and enveloping angle. Its softness is widely appreciated in the Far East, land of wisdom. 

Cardamom, Sage, Pink Peppercorn, Lychee, Rose, Hawtorn, Peony, Ambrette Seed, Sandal Wood, Musk

name: SOUTH BAY - COLOGNE
description:
SUNNY, VIBRATING, INTENSE

SOUTH BAY
90ml Refillable Bottle

Contemporary Haute Parfumerie created by Jean-Claude Ellena and Thierry De Baschmakoff.

A Party Fragrance in Miami:
Intensely sparkling, this eau de Toilette  unveils a woody architecture behind it’s fres head notes. The heart is based on the Grapefruit wood which brings backbone to the perfume. A touch of daim in the bottom notes splendidly underlines the Sandalwood.  

Grapefruit, Mandarine Leafs, Tamarine, Grapefruit tree, Eglantine, Freesia, Sandal Wood, Vetiver, Daim

name: AFTER MIDNIGHT - COLOGNE
description:
SENSUAL, ENVELOPING, ATYPICAL

AFTER MIDNIGHT
90ml Refillable Bottle

Contemporary Haute Parfumerie created by Jean-Claude Ellena and Thierry De Baschmakoff.

In The Heart of the Night:
This sensual Cologne has to be worn at night to reveal all its charms. A dense luminous and shining fragrance, with intoxicating spices gets smoother along the way on a amber and sensual base that keeps its promises. For those who dare a lustful cologne. 

Bergamot, Angelica roots, Neroli, Iris, Lentisc, White jasmine, Labdanum, Benzoin, Amber wood.
